reviews.review_text: Hauling Ass from 'chester Had to, or we'd miss the show. The boys (crew) actually passed us doing 90 mph. Again this version is just spectacular. Enjpot the Fall of '80

tripped out Excellent Half Step>Franklin's, Let It Grow, High Time and Sailor>Saint. 
9/2 and 9/6 are the best from '80.

Best of the bunch This September run was great (though I think 12/30/80 is my favorite from the year--the China Doll!).  Good show here, though.
This recording is the best of the bunch, I think.  Better even than the always dependable Wise recording also available here.
bread crumb This is a peerless audience recording.  Peer - less.
